A [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] '''scout ship''' was a [[Starship/Legends|ship]] used by [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] and [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] while scouting out locations for a new Rebel Alliance base shortly after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]]. [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]] found the vessel on [[Jarnollen]] and [[Mission to Jarnollen|destroyed]] it, though the Rebels were not inside.

